data.description: This charming and beautifully updated home features a bright and open floor plan, tons of natural light and an extra bonus room on the main floor and below grade! Large open kitchen with newer stainless steel appliances and elegant French doors off the dining area lead to a large wood deck overlooking the huge 1/4 acre backyard. Lots of room and options for a big garden, additional parking and a 20x30 existing cement slab. Extra room below grade that provides ample space for a Rec Room, additional storage, potential bedroom, etc. Beautiful home and yard to enjoy! Water heater and appliances new 4 yrs ago. Sellers are willing to pay up to $8000 towards buyer closing costs and prepaids!
